1.to get max element in array -->
  Using .maxOrNull()
  This method returns the maximum element in the array or null if the array is empty.

2.to get sqrt -->
  Using sqrt() on a number

3.stringstream -->
  val input = "word1 word2 word3"
  val words = input.split(" ") // Splits the string by spaces i.e. a delimeter
  
  for (word in words) {
      println(word) 
  }
4.power --> only works for double so need to type convert
  Math.pow(base, exponent)
  OR
  base.pow(exponent)

